Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.87,0:00:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,小霞 你的发夹好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,被你发现啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.01,0:00:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟今天就是最后一天了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.01,0:00:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要好好加把劲才行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.68,0:00:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.51,0:00:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一转眼就是最后一天了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.27,0:00:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,表演是12点开始 还有一些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.68,0:00:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之前 大家先一起去逛文化节吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.06,0:00:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,担当开场表演的是岚珠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.78,0:00:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.57,0:00:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这么短的时间 她就成为了学校的大红人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.45,0:00:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,希望她能为我们带来开门红
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.99,0:00:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.83,0:00:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这一天终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你们至今为止的表演 我都看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.72,0:00:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,每一场都非常精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.87,0:01:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 今天的主角并不是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.51,0:01:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,而是我 钟岚珠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.81,0:01:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就像一开始说好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.81,0:01:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我会在这个学园偶像季上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,让你们见识到 什么才是最棒的个人偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.77,0:01:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那可真是让人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.86,0:01:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,小霞霞也不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.36,0:01:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.24,0:01:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,璃奈板板 干劲满满
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.03,0:01:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就让我们用棒的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.33,0:01:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,让今天成为所有人心中最棒的回忆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.46,0:01:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.26,0:01:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,最后的曲子…还空着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.68,0:01:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我们还没有定下来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.51,0:01:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想让侑前辈写一首能让同好会一起唱的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.06,0:01:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但她好像遇到了困难
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.73,0:02:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来确实没有看到她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.77,0:03:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你想去哪儿逛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我想看你们班的摊子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.28,0:04:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,爱姐了解 那我们就出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,大家请看这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,现在即将开启校内彩虹滑道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,作为今天上午的一大看点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,虹学号将沿着流水素面同好会监修的滑道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,在校园内绕行一周
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.31,0:04:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.47,0:04:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.64,0:04:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,虹学号首先会经过中央出入口 前往西区
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来 它将改变航线 前往东区
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.33,0:04:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,真是大工程啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,在小船到达终点的同时 小岚珠的表演也会开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也要去给她加油才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:04:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一块蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.39,0:05:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,步梦真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.15,0:05:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 小侑联系过你们了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.99,0:05:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,她是不是还在烦恼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.49,0:05:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在还没法去找她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会帮你去看看的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.54,0:05:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,包在我们身上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,小栞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.26,0:05:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说高咲同学遇到了困难
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.72,0:05:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你真体贴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,小侑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.27,0:05:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,岚珠的表演马上要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,悸动在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,悸动…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:05:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,悸动…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么想都出不来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎么想…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,完全悸不出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.45,0:06:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这比想象中的还要没救
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,看来需要转换一下心情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.67,0:06:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我也要跟你们一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.47,0:06:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃的东西就要跟大家一起分享
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.77,0:06:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.36,0:06:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,别看我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.66,0:06:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,喝了这个 冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.25,0:06:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:06:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,小侑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:06:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,放心 我不是身体不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,明明已经找大家商量了这么多次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不过是商量 多少次都没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.23,0:07:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,说来听听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.48,0:07:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,为了好不容易举办的偶像季 要作个好曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我想尽自己所能做到最好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,一想到如何才能向观众传达大家的优点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.58,0:07:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,如何才能让粉丝们喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,作为给小岚珠的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这首曲子是否能成为我留在同好会的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,想到要同时实现以上的种种
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.89,0:07:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我就没了信心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,然后就越想越混乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:07:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你太过用力了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.65,0:08:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,而且也想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.32,0:08:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,很像你的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我来说不太适合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.66,0:08:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,其实你并不用想这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起来唱你写的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.42,0:08:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,光是这样就已经很棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.38,0:08:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,能唱侑写的歌 我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.59,0:08:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,小霞霞和大家会挺起胸膛在舞台上唱出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.31,0:08:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,果然还是应该写一首
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.81,0:08:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,能够回应同好会的大家和粉丝心中悸动的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉马上就能完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:09:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,表演马上就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,小岚珠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来给你加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.35,0:09:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,彩虹滑道终于要进入最高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.93,0:09:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,只要顺利到达终点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,学园偶像季的主舞台就会被华丽点亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.11,0:09:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,开始表演
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.36,0:09:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就要到终点了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,绕学校一周 虹学号来到了最后的滑道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.99,0:09:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,终点就在眼前…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.92,0:09:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.96,0:09:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,彩排的时候明明很顺利的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.59,0:09:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,停下了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,小岚珠…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.64,0:10:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来就没指望别人帮我做开场准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,之前也说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我只要当给予的那方就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我是为了证明自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,才站上这个舞台的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.28,0:10:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,因为 我只有这一个选择
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.93,0:11:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,很精彩 岚珠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.81,0:11:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都不知道 原来你也想当学园偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 我已经习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来轮到你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.28,0:11:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我很期待你们的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.37,0:11:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,确实孤傲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是个人偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,岚珠的表演比之前更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.22,0:11:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这下有压力了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是时候该准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:11:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,小米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是米娅前辈 才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.42,0:12:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚小岚珠的表演 让我十分悸动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.76,0:12:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我也说不清
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但是从她的歌声和舞蹈中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.18,0:12:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以感受到她独一无二的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.19,0:12:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那个瞬间 小岚珠填满了我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,岚珠是最棒的表演者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:13:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不只是她 其他学园偶像一定也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.12,0:13:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,将自己的一切倾注到表演中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.67,0:13:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是她们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们没必要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.01,0:13:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,只要按照他人的要求作曲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,得到大家的好评不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.27,0:13:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要为同好会的偶像们写曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.94,0:13:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.23,0:13:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一定都会喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.95,0:13:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,真的…是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.12,0:13:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,侑前辈没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.50,0:13:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,一定没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.71,0:13:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就把自己分内的事做好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.63,0:13:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,或许这么做 大家也会喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但我此时感受到的这份悸动…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.27,0:14:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是更加…该怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我…身为粉丝的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,其实并不只是为了偶像们的表演和歌声悸动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.97,0:14:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,步梦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,小雪菜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,小雫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.47,0:14:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.06,0:14:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,果林
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,小霞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.98,0:14:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,小璃奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.77,0:14:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,艾玛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我是为大家全力展现自我的样子而悸动的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我想更靠近大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,和大家一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.58,0:15:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,去展现此时此刻的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.84,0:15:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我的悸动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你认真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.52,0:15:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的要这么做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我想根据这个重新编曲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.28,0:15:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你愿意帮我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是 我想在同好会做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.37,0:15:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是 我想和学园偶像们一起实现的 梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,非常棒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.69,0:16:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.36,0:16:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,另外 我有一件事想做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,和文化节一起举办五天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.93,0:16:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,学园偶像季也终于来到了最后一天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.52,0:16:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要向参与其中的学校们 学园偶像们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.44,0:17:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,还有来到现场的观众们 说一声谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.53,0:17:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来就是最后一首歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.91,0:17:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们最重要的伙伴为我们写的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.04,0:17:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来我们要唱的这首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这个舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.21,0:17:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,全都多亏了至今相遇的各位才得以实现
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.51,0:17:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是许多的相遇给了我们力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.89,0:17:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,正因为有人帮助我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这首新歌才会诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,正因为有人建议我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.06,0:17:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这次的偶像季才会得以实现
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.19,0:17:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,正因为有人让我们看到了精彩的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们才会更加茁壮成长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,正因为有聚集在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,愿意爱着学园偶像的各位在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:18:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们才能顺利迎来偶像季的终曲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,然后这里又会诞生出下一个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.22,0:18:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,就让我们一起向前奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.85,0:18:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来 敬请欣赏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.64,0:21:23.97,TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HCC60D3&\fad(500,0)\pos(1042.223,701.778)}第8集 彩虹绽放的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.01,0:21:23.97,TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HCC60D3&\fad(500,0)\fs20\pos(1072.889,674.222)}悸动追梦人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.09,0:22:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.22,0:22:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,大家真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.89,0:23:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.10,0:23:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.43,0:23:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,小岚珠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.68,0:23:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你的表演很精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.39,0:23:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,都是多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.36,0:23:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经感受到了你的决心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.61,0:23:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你们也用精彩的表演证明了自己是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.28,0:23:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经全力以赴了 但你们比我付出更多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.87,0:23:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这一趟来的很值
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.50,0:23:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经没有遗憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.55,0:23:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.67,0:23:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 我无法触及的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:31.25,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1\fs35}刻不待时！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:35.50,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1\fs35}未知的世界 正悄然来临的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.89,0:10:39.68,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1\fs35}把常识抛到九霄云外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:42.83,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1\fs35}这条路我会亲手开创
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:44.50,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1\fs35}然后把你握在手心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:49.31,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1\fs35}不需要命令！我不会允许！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:31.25,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}The golden time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:35.50,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}始まる予感 未知なる世界が
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.89,0:10:39.68,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}常識なんて拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:42.83,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}I make! 切り開くの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:44.50,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}手に入れてみせるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:49.31,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}指図はno! 我不会允许!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.89,0:10:57.35,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1\fs35}欢迎光临 女王圣域
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:02.79,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1\fs35}你或否有所耳闻？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:05.08,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1\fs35}我就是你最对的人!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:07.88,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1\fs35}任谁都会倾心的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:09.65,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1\fs35}是的 我独一无二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.89,0:10:57.35,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}Welcome to the queendom
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:02.79,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}噂で聞いた?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:05.08,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}まさに私が that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:07.88,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}誰もが憧れちゃうの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:09.65,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}Yes, I'm so special
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.87,0:19:24.30,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs35}蓬勃而出的是这份悸动 绚烂夺目的是这份闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:28.84,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs35}就在 从那一天变幻而成的世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.59,0:19:34.52,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs35}远远观望仍不足惜 动身起来靠近你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:39.31,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs35}就在这里 尽我所能 去寻找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:45.74,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs35}这就是梦想吗？ 是像梦想般炫彩的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:49.95,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs35}仅仅诉说它 就会情绪高涨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.95,0:19:56.37,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs35}这一定就是梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.37,0:20:00.88,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs35}它让我们充满了勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:04.55,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs35}在雀跃中完成的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:07.26,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs35}情节如何 全靠我们书写
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:12.55,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs35}仅仅是遇见你 这就已经是一个奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.55,0:20:15.26,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs35}在雀跃中完成的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.26,0:20:17.89,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs35}让我们变得欢快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.89,0:20:21.81,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs35}从心底呼喊出活着的愉悦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.81,0:20:23.98,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs35}你也想要这样的感觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.98,0:20:28.28,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs35}想与你一同雀跃 想与你一同出发
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:31.66,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs35}开始吧！你也来一同雀跃！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.87,0:19:24.30,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs40}生まれたのはトキメキ 惹かれたのは輝き
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:28.84,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs40}あの日から変わりはじめた世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.59,0:19:34.52,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs40}見てるだけじゃ足りない カラダ動かして
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:39.31,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs40}できることないか 探してみようよここで
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:45.74,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs40}これは夢かな？ 夢ってステキな言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:49.95,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs40}言ってるだけでイイ気分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.95,0:19:56.37,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs40}きっと夢だと決めてしまえ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.37,0:20:00.88,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs40}ああっ勇気が湧いてきた！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:04.55,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs40}ワクワク叶える物語
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:07.26,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs40}どうなるかは僕ら次第
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:12.55,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs40}出会いって それだけで奇跡と思うんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.55,0:20:15.26,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs40}ワクワク叶える物語
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.26,0:20:17.89,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs40}みんなで楽しくなろうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.89,0:20:21.81,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs40}生きてる！ってココロが叫んじゃう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.81,0:20:23.98,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs40}そんな実感欲しいよねっ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.98,0:20:28.28,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs40}ワクワクしたいキミと ワクワク発ストーリー
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:31.66,INALL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2\blur2\fs40}始まれ！ ワクワクしようキミも！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
